Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:34.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「いま！」という　この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:39.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なんだって　音楽に　出来たらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:44.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ　全力で　やり切ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:47.07,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔し涙　拭ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:50.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春のフレージング
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:55.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡が　努力の　先にあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:01:01.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限界は　あたしが決める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:03.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:10.34,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一回　大げさな夢を　探しにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:13.95,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止めない　勇気こそ　強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:20.74,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何百回　挑戦かさねて　ここまで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:25.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}チャンスの神様　みててね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:27.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:30.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}離したくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:33.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}輝きに変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:38.45,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いよ　届け…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:34.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「此时此刻」的这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:39.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望能以音乐将其铭刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:44.35,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还未拼尽全力到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:47.07,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断拭去的悔恨泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:50.60,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是青春的分句
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:55.63,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是努力之后便会有奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:01:01.32,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那极限由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:03.48,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}吹响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:10.34,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次去追寻那庞大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:13.95,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强大就是永不放弃的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:20.74,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经历数百次的挑战　来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:25.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请机会之神看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:27.72,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想忘记的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:30.39,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不愿放开的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:33.42,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}变为耀眼的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:38.45,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将这份心意　传递出去…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------EDCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.76,0:22:25.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}割り切れない想いを力に変えてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:29.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無謀だと笑われた　何度も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:33.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}毎日が冒険で　青春で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:38.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい音と出会っては磨いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:42.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}本気でやったからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:46.95,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こわい瞬間もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:47.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:48.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:49.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:50.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}叶えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:55.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一度息を吹き込む　明日へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:59.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}タクトに導かれてここまで来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:03.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたと来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.30,0:23:05.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でているのは人生だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:07.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響くのは感情だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:12.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと忘れないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:16.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}光る音が涙を照らしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:20.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}辛いことばかりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.50,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だっていつも　いつも楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:28.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そうでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:32.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！歌え　五線の上で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:39.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！響け　遠くの春に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.76,0:22:25.26,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春的苦涩变为了前进的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:29.64,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}年少冲动让我无数次被嘲笑声掩埋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:33.48,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每天都在冒险　挥洒青春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:38.23,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断磨练期待与新的乐声邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:42.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正因为全身心的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:46.95,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自然会有害怕的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:47.76,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要传递
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:48.66,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:49.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:50.24,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:55.12,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次向着奏响的明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:59.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遵循指挥棒的指引来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:03.30,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.30,0:23:05.76,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正在奏响的是人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:07.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}余音缭绕的是情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:12.72,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直都无法忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:16.52,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}耀眼的乐声将我们的泪水照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:20.98,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}并非全是辛酸经历
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.50,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为　一路走来有许多快乐伴随着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:28.41,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:32.12,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！于五线谱之上唱响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:39.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！向着远处胜利的春天吹响吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------------PART--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.07,0:00:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟他妻子去世以后  就一直没有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师说他们没在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这演奏让人提不起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她无法忍受希美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关西大赛上各校的演奏顺序已经下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保佑我们不是第一个出场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:02:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们北宇治高中是第16个出场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,23所学校中第16个出场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  其他高中的出场顺序是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那些主流强校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大阪东照是前半第3个出场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀塔大学附属第12个出场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  明静工科是在我们前面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第15个出场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然紧接着明静之后！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  知道在强校之后登场就怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有点忌惮…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必在意  不必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关西大赛无弱校  排哪都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像桥本老师说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只要像平时一样去演奏就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离关西大赛还剩10天不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是没能把从明日香学姐那听来的事告诉希美学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:14.30,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1020,720)\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}觉醒的双簧管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还会再练一会吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铠冢同学  现在有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  在听到你独奏的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也搞到了有些不足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  想到你是高中生觉得这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擅自把你的可能性上限给框死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了很失礼的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的演奏技术非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何听着让人感觉有些沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以再愉快点去演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  麻美子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和爸爸稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个部分  你试试再加大吸气吹吹看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能有感情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:04:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想太多也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就试着照自己喜欢的吹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去外面吹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得集中精神才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次吹得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  你来得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去见明日香学姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再练习开始前再找她说说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  现在关西大赛已经临近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉在大赛前再这样找她会妨碍到她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和夏纪也提过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是放弃回归了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想在最后为明日香学姐尽点绵力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来霙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一个人在音乐教师里对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铠冢学姐吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  刚才只听到有双簧管的声音传出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:06:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说老师叫她吹得再有感情一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此  她正在为独奏的事犯愁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她虽然性格冷谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但演奏是非常有热情的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是演奏出愉悦的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给人一种情感爆发的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  所以被这样说我很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看她的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  糟了  糟了  糟了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹长笛的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会有事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好的预感在脑中挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须想个办法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的决定好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  今天是最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后在大赛结束前我都不会再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  要怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我考虑这些的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:08:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铠冢学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  希美她做什么了要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才生气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之得快点去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她的情况的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能去找一下霙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在要是遇见应付不来的人会很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才生气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:09:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀揣着不好的预感和忐忑的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个接一个教室地寻找她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为讨厌希美学姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是被说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美她没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我害怕见到希美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我害怕面对现实…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最珍视的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅长和人交流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性格阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  铠冢同学你有参加社团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是归宅部  什么都没有参加咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美和这样的我成为了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为希美的邀请  我才加入了吹奏部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时真的很高兴  每天都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对希美来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是她朋友中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,众多朋友中的一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那回…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时连她退部的事也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  今天希美没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是退部了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时只有我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她什么都没和我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕自己对她来说只是一个陌路人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白自己为什么会在吹奏部里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样为什么还要坚持呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只有乐器是我和希美之间羁绊的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不出话来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想过会有人因为这样的理由而演奏乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我这么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在害怕和希美说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…对我来说…希美就是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被她拒绝的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被拒绝的话就没别人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说  我算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为觉得我可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才对我这么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会同情我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是个笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去和自己讨厌的人一起行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会强迫自己和人套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同情？那是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙你之前就没把我当成朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社团也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的只是为了希美才一直坚持吹奏乐的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那样努力地练习  以竞赛会为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就没有从中感受到什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在府大赛中获得关西大赛的参赛资格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就没有感到开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路坚持下来太值了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力没有白费
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉自己终于能从中学的阴影中解放出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就没有任何感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也觉得很对不起那些退部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的能为此开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  霙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好和她说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐让我把这个带来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是做了什么让你不开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这人很笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全想不出头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有和我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你退部的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没必要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你一直很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我很颓废的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有一个人在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也在一个人练习
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「一起退部吧」这种话怎么说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才没和我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你一直觉得自己被我排挤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会那么想  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想错了  我没有那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要和我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在逃避…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己胡思乱想…一个人在那害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  我呢去看了府大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常震撼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听了  你的独奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从中学开始就很喜欢你的双簧管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放佛内心被牢牢抓住一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想听你演奏的双簧管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望你能听我演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的乐声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能吹得那么优美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来霙的演奏一直是为希美而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是赢不了希美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都和霙在一起一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美是比你好100倍的好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起你也许要好500倍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  我很庆幸霙的身边有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在安慰我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦  被害羞  被害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪对我好温柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说那么恶心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本想在竞赛会结束前不让她们见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过霙的性格也很自私呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙之所以对希美那么执着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来只是害怕孤独一人不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而优子是她的备胎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种说法…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人还真是以利已为准则行动的生物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得明日香学姐你考虑得太深刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深刻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一起去全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟什么是真心话  什么是表面功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条分界线实在过于暧昧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她究竟以何种角度在看问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些害怕去思考这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你去哪了弄得那么脏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有想过自己是为了某个人在吹奏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非要说的话  是为了自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈  还是那个丽奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思  你是在戏弄我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  下一首乐曲开始了
